						Q . <span>메이플 렙 몇?</span>
					</div>
					<textarea class="p-2 col-10"
						style="background-color: #f0f0f066; border: #b1b1b1 solid 1px; height: 100px"
						placeholder="답변을 작성해 주세요"></textarea>
				</div>
				<div class="col-12 my-3 mb-4" style="text-align: center">
